        Encodes the market by order response. Returns success if encoding succeeds or failure if encoding fails.
        Parameters:
        itemReqInfo - - The item request related info
        isSolicited - - The response is solicited if set
        msgBuf - - The message buffer to encode the market price response into
        serviceId - - The service id of the market price response
        dictionary - - The dictionary used for encoding
        error - - error in case of encoding failure
        cacheInfo - - cache info to determine if cache data
        cacheEntry - - cache entry where to retrieve or apply data from/to cache
